This is too funny.  For those who can't tell, the reason I said &quot;what???&quot; repedeately is because it just pisses the fuck out of whoever is whining, as proven by this thread he made.<br>
<br>
Just because im bored and killin' time i'll explain what happened.  I setup camp at the front end of the caves, it was fully popped, Jhardzia and ghetto-friend (don't remember who it was, nor do I care) were sitting there like shark tits.  So I charm a mob, and commense ownage.  Halfway through the clear Jhardzia runs in to try and gank some mobs, I believe there is something to be said for respecting my camp, let alone trying to leech off of someone by waiting for them to &quot;Break&quot; or &quot;clear&quot; some of the area to make it easier for you.  <br>
<br>
So I simply laid down the /deny and cockblocked him from doing so.  His pussy then promptly started bleeding.  As Saalron said, you just gotta be smart, I showed him I meant business by ganking the first 2 or 3 mobs he tried to pull from my camp.  Then when he kindly told me a petition was sent, I stopped, low and behold, this covers my ass since a GM/Guide must witness it.  Thanks much for the forewarning Jhardzia!  <br>
<br>
Although, even though I stopped, Jhardzia was such a cock slut that he tried to pull, but got 2+ because I wasn't there to clear for him and he had to zone.  Too bad so sad.  I picked up his train, cleared it for XP, and resumed :P<br>
<br>
Then for some unknown reason he sent tells like &quot;Let's take this outside!&quot; im like wtf? This is a fuckin' game.  So apparently he wanted to go to a PVP arena and kill me to get satisfaction.  Whatever, I have never practiced PVP so I know I would probably lose, and have no interest in jiggling his balls.  At this point I left to a raid so I don't know if he went into convulsions or wiped to the camp since I wasn't there to be his safety net or what.<br>
<br>
Point being, I was simply protecting my camp that he was trying to leech out of.  Albeit there &quot;Are no camps&quot;, to me there's common courtesy of the cave camps and i'll protect it.  I won't be a fluffy bunny and whine to you to leave, or petition, i'll just fuckin' cockblock you to piss you off and get my way.<br>
<br>
Lesson learned Jhardzia? Eat fuck.<br>
